Executive Profile
Norman J. Abdallah  Chief Executive Officer, President and Director, Del Frisco's Restaurant Group, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 5 different industries.See Board Relationships54$2,179,252As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Norman J. Abdallah has been Chief Executive Officer since 21st November 2016 and President since November 2016 of Del Frisco's Restaurant Group, Inc. Mr. Abdallah has been Chief Executive Officer of Romano's Macaroni Grill Inc. since July 2010. He serves as a Principal at Triple Tap Ventures LLC. He served as the Chief Executive Officer and President of Restaurants Unlimited, Inc. from March 2009 to July 8, 2010. He co-founded Fired Up, Inc. in 1997 and served as ... its President since January 2005 and also its Chief Executive Officer from 1997 to 2008. He has over 25 years of restaurant, franchise and concept development experience to Triple Tap. He was employed with Brinker International for nine years serving in various management positions including Vice President of Franchise Operations and Development, where he was responsible for the worldwide franchise programs of Chili's, Macaroni Grill and On the Border. He served as the President and Chief Executive Officer of Red Hot Concepts, a Chili's licensee for the United Kingdom, Australia and New Zealand. He has been an Independent Director of Del Frisco's Restaurant Group, Inc. since July 2012 and served as its Member of Advisory Board from March 2011 to July 2012. Mr. Abdallah served as a Member of the Board of Directors at California Pizza Kitchen, Inc. since 2011.Read Full Background




