Insider Activity


Individual




Norman J. Abdallah



Mr. Norman J. Abdallah is Chairman at Triple Tap Ventures LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Del Frisco's Restaurant Group, Inc. and California Pizza Kitchen, Inc. 
Mr. Abdallah was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer by Counter Concepts LLC, Chief Executive Officer by Mac Acquisition of Kansas LLC, President & Chief Executive Officer by Restaurants Unlimited, Inc., President & Co-Chief Executive Officer by Fired Up, Inc., a Principal by Brinker International, Inc., and President & Chief Executive Officer by Red Hot Concepts, Inc.



