				Abdallah Is New Romano’s CEO




			Published on Wednesday, 21 July 2010		
 
						
							Written by Averra Admin					

Romano’s Macaroni Grill named Norman Abdallah its chief executive officer and Carey Carrington its chief financial officer. Brad Blum, chief executive officer, and Bob Mock, chief operating officer, left Romano’s Macaroni Grill to pursue other interests, according to a company release.
Abdallah and Carrington have a combined 30 years of senior leadership experience in the restaurant industry.





















































